title: Do Rioters seriously play with people to get their 100th normal win?
body:
EDIT: I MEANT 1000th!!!!!

Basically the title! I would LOVE to spend an evening with some EUNE Rioters and talk about stuff ^^ I'm kinda late though - sitting at ~1050 wins... I've just got to know about this thing though - so maybe there's still a chance :)

Would love to hear an answer from a Riot employee
